title: Felipe Gustavo on skateboarding, his dad, and the Olympics
description: Legendary skateboarder Felipe Gustavo joined the Olympic Channel Podcast to talk about his career, how his dad sold his car to fund his first big contest entry, and why staying humble is so important.
